ctures, our model improves performance in downstream tasks like cross-modal retrieval, missing view imputation, and causal discovery across domains. Moreover, the structured variational approach allows uncertainty quantification in both shared and specific subspaces, enabling reliable decision-making in safety-critical applications.",
